description: Returns the tags for the specified SageMaker resource.

parameters.name: ResourceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource whose tags you want to retrieve.

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: An array of Tag objects, each with a tag key and a value.

nested_items.name: Key
nested_items.description: The tag key. Tag keys must be unique per resource.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If response is truncated, SageMaker includes a token in the response. You can use this token in your subsequent request to fetch next set of tokens.
